window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Conquest-Obsessed Ants. Chisels. Lasers.</b></p> <p>After turning the world of AstroTerra upside down, Roth has no choice but to leave the verdant landscape of Green Country and venture off to the inhospitable Rock Canyon, a land of cliffs and slavers.</p> <p>Roth ends up finding a mysterious city filled with exciting sights. He makes new friends and finds a place where he can finally craft and play peacefully. Regardless of how much Roth tries to run, trouble keeps finding him.</p> <p>Why can't he just lie low? Why does he keep causing chaos wherever he goes? Enjoy the new installment in this funny series rife with adventure and follow Roth and Lin's journey as they explore more of the incredible virtual world of AstroTerra</p> <p><i>Hidden Class: Pacifist is a whimsical LitRPG series set in a sci-fi fantasy cyberpunk world. If you like ant colonies, leatherworking, and lasers, join Roth on his journey!</i></p>"; 
